{"id": "1411707473076817950", "channel_id": "1408363615488180256", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "シールドが弱い。エリカは0.5人分のディフェンダーなので、カーシアを外してナウティラにするといいかな。", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T13:41:29.838000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408363615488180256", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超次元の攻略方法", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1411710930277896212", "channel_id": "1408363615488180256", "type": 0, "author_id": "369716191339479040", "author_name": "tokitoto", "author_bot": false, "content": "カレンoutのナウティラinとかでもいいかも", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T13:55:14.099000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408363615488180256", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超次元の攻略方法", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1411711112746893443", "channel_id": "1408363615488180256", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "カレン外すと回復おらんようになって詰むかも。", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T13:55:57.603000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408363615488180256", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超次元の攻略方法", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1411711197606187128", "channel_id": "1408363615488180256", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "何気に静観をボックスに入れておくのも強いっちゃ強いので", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T13:56:17.835000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408363615488180256", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超次元の攻略方法", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1411713467844399125", "channel_id": "1408363615488180256", "type": 0, "author_id": "369716191339479040", "author_name": "tokitoto", "author_bot": false, "content": "どうなんでしょう、闇の境界の4くらいなら回復なくても平気なような。私が日本版で回復欲しいなってなったのは融災の難易度4とかになってからでした。\nグロ版では回復どうこうというよりカレンが単純に便利なので入れてるんですが日本版だとあまりカレンにパワーを感じず……。", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T14:05:19.102000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408363615488180256", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超次元の攻略方法", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1411716495121059891", "channel_id": "1408363615488180256", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "うーん、静観でタイミング悪く手札に来ちゃった集結を打つタイミングずらしたり、", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T14:17:20.861000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408363615488180256", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超次元の攻略方法", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1411716674926674002", "channel_id": "1408363615488180256", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "おまけで毒ばらまいたり、料理でコストは生成できるから日本版でも外せなくなってます", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T14:18:03.730000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-31T14:18:32.428000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408363615488180256", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超次元の攻略方法", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
